### GET all articles (admin - EN title)
GET http://localhost:8080/api/articles

### GET all articles with pagination
GET http://localhost:8080/api/articles?page=0&size=5&sortBy=createdAt&sortDir=desc

### GET published articles (public)
GET http://localhost:8080/api/articles/published

### GET published articles with filter
GET http://localhost:8080/api/articles/published?language=ZH

### GET published articles with keyword search
GET http://localhost:8080/api/articles/published?keyword=AI&language=EN

### GET article list (admin)
GET http://localhost:8080/api/articles?page=0&size=10&sortBy=createdAt&sortDir=desc